{"tid":1915350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要必睇] 黑警新拉人策略","createTime":"2020-03-08T07:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T11:35:10.000Z","uid":324163,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"0b43594bf89e60fe7cbcacfd1906413be2a883a9","tid":1915350,"uid":324163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:04:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>黑警狂拉前線手足，恐嚇+虐打迫供 推到所有手足都要知<br />\n</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n有朋友最近被拉上埋法庭<br />\n邊單唔講，但唔係預約被捕，但閪9手法好撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同尋晚水晶之夜應該係一撚樣<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">閪9手法</span></span></strong><br />\n便衣9上門會先拍門，講到好輕，會請協助調查(班閪9無搜查令)<br />\n如果唔理班9，佢地就會開始<span style=\"color: maroon;\">恐嚇</span><br />\n講話會日日上黎，叫佢全家小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話出街睇住等等<br />\n<br />\n有人就問班閪9點會知手足住係邊<br />\n預約被捕就無野好講<br />\n俾9跟都無辦法(閪9在暗，唯有自己小心d)<br />\n依家連安全屋都會出事(熟人篤灰)<br />\n之後再講有咩方法可以盡量降低被跟蹤同保障自己既機會<br />\n<br />\n總之閪9會恐嚇到你或家人去開門<br />\n開左門就係班9既天下<br />\n去到依個moment就唯有乖乖地合作<br />\n同佢地合作既係：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">我無野講!!!唔知，唔清楚!!!我無野講!!!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">拉到返9屋</span></span></strong><br />\n班9就會進行<span style=\"color: maroon;\">精神</span>同<span style=\"color: maroon;\">肉體施虐</span><br />\n從而迫你<ins>認罪 + 篤灰</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n精神方面就一定係恐嚇會搞你屋企人/搵人搞你屋企人<br />\n用手足既仁愛同大義去勒索<br />\n恐嚇完唔得就會<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">打</span></strong><br />\n點打法朋友已經無詳細講，但應該係唔想記起<br />\n都有明顯既傷痕，點處理就交俾律師去做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">降低被跟蹤同保障自己既方法</span></strong></span><br />\n被跟蹤，之前應該有好多建議post出過<br />\n離不開<ins>不斷遊走，搵障礙掩護再走</ins><br />\n返到屋企禁<ins>lift唔好禁自己個層，禁多幾層再行樓梯行上行落</ins><br />\n總之<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">唔好用實同一方法，每次都轉一轉<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>熟人篤灰安全屋都出事</strong></span></span><br />\n無法得知熟人點篤灰<br />\n但唔係人人都堅持到被恐嚇同被班閪9打<br />\n我朋友最後都頂唔順被人打到要認罪，但就無供到同伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>閪9拍門保障自己</strong></span></span><br />\n拍得門，就即係班9擺明黎拉你<br />\n一定要保持冷靜<br />\n首先默默念幾次口訣：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">我無野講，唔清楚，唔知，我無野講!!!</span></strong></span><br />\n然後盡量<strong><ins>開cam</ins></strong>，或者<strong><ins>錄音</ins></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">但d cam同錄音都要盡量隱藏好! </span></strong>盡量記錄整個過程，最好有方法係一路錄低，一路upload到上cloud server或者開live咁<br />\n求巴絲提供最好同埋最平價方法可以咁做 (據我所知ssp賣cam個d 幾舊水有個大6牌子既 cam，仲可以upload上佢地既cloud，要俾$，幾十蚊可以保存到1個月，收音功能都唔錯)<br />\n然後<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">打定電話俾信任既人聽自己將會被捕，叫佢幫手搵定律師</span></strong><br />\n依個moment，就算班9無搜查令，你開唔開門都無分別<br />\n班閪9已經無所不用其極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以最好既方法就係<ins>保障自己</ins>，同埋最好<ins>錄到佢地既一舉一動</ins><br />\n佢地入到屋，搵到依d就一定會熄左佢or破壞佢，一定唔會俾你捉到佢地既衰野，<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">所以點樣backup就要各位巴絲幫手諗方法</span></strong><br />\n(暫時諗到既方法，歡迎大家集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />思廣益)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">拉番9屋被迫供</span></strong></span><br />\n就算律師幾快到，班閪9一定會用盡方法阻止律師即時搵到你<br />\n所以<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">預左有幾個鐘一定會被9施虐</span></strong><br />\n唔係話嚇大家，朋友真人經歷，依d一定要講出黎，等大家有心理準備<br />\n最好當然係堅持到最後一刻<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「我無野講，唔清楚，唔知，我無野講!!!」</span></strong></span><br />\n但如果都係頂唔順，又可以點做?<br />\n我都無答案俾到大家<br />\n朋友就認左罪無再講其他野<br />\n相信坐係電腦前面既連登大神一定會話渣ga<br />\n但人就係會有軟弱既一面<br />\n會唔會頂唔順既時候，供一個藍絲朋友，可以得到一個喘息機會，可以等到律師成功黎見到你? 歡迎大家集思廣益!<br />\n我諗過<span style=\"color: green;\">如果真係要供，供一個藍絲朋友，但講既資料唔可以講得多，愈少愈好</span>，即係俾d hints班狗，等佢地自己查，拖佢地時間<br />\n例如淨係講<span style=\"color: green;\">佢個名，電話，大概住邊<br />\n講話幾時見到佢 (最好係合法遊行俾閪9腰斬既日子)</span>，講自己係合法遊行見到佢，之後就分開左，知佢上前線咁個類，自己個日就有事係腰斬前走左咁<br />\n我唔知咁樣得唔得，可唔可以拎到喘息既時間<br />\n因為朋友覺得佢自己住安全屋都俾9上門係應該有熟人講左出黎<br />\n但佢都明白俾9打真係唔好受<br />\n所以都求大家集思廣益!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a28479ac7cec5314f53b23ab9727b92978b39ef","tid":1915350,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:06:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2f637dbd149765dfb2ed4299ed6fb4cbce2a966e","tid":1915350,"uid":52228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:07:57.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"e809f1225b93b603e1963790c8ac60a0927cec0a","tid":1915350,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc4d2bd6abdae4a4455eed4ea842e1480b43859","tid":1915350,"uid":205372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8116e04899ae8ab5e36376b4351ffc149368744","tid":1915350,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:11:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c52f14a0e3304246514ceee4501ad3bc06a41b20","tid":1915350,"uid":67049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"諗定幾個藍屍朋友到時自救呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb25bfc6f8f94a99d1775b6fd10c7a03458e847","tid":1915350,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:15:28.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0721583292f0e85263ada621529928816243195","tid":1915350,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7729b67eeced6ebc5f6facd03aa1b42ac945595f","tid":1915350,"uid":64333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:16:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a729548b30edef8f9f9b0fc8998ee1b09242e67","tid":1915350,"uid":310765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b63d8e56cc4e73ceaee420656c340f89bd088c4b","tid":1915350,"uid":30367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9bb8c7dda342ffea2ae5a74f93f898fc47059d","tid":1915350,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:19:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7bae8ab6a447ea47f3b947a30739e2272909365c","tid":1915350,"uid":294031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:23:23.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推"},{"pid":"905f79d4e1aff59a62af59ef1cae82c68655e956","tid":1915350,"uid":207833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:24:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"449eef14464ff2258b0640657239a28a9f9c336a","tid":1915350,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"329f7413268da422b2a7f4dfeea01539e9c82f3a","tid":1915350,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:25:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8c7d5071f9aa57fc0f89d93cb616b1a5eaf77794","tid":1915350,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f27b50db871e3dee7306fc4bf767853850f13f8","tid":1915350,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:27:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"195f532d2f82d0787c468d615384eb26feba0515","tid":1915350,"uid":118330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T07:28:48.000Z","msg